[This outbreak is certainly likely to be foodborne. Many jail facilities in large cities have central locations for food preparations so outbreaks can affect multiple sites. It is possible that if all the cases were at one location that the cause was with issues with food storage after preparation.

A map of Chicago, Illinois, United States: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=5791825,520. - Mod.LL]
